---
import CTA from './CTA.astro';
import BenefitsCard from './BenefitsCard.astro';
import Section from './Section.astro';
import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components';
---

<Section id="features">
  <div class="container flex flex-col gap-y-16 items-baseline relative z-[3]">
    <h2 class="font-title font-bold uppercase text-4xl leading-[44px]">
      <span class="pt-BR">
        Veja as <span class="text-[#FF3158] underline">vantagens</span> de ser
        um RD
      </span>
      <span class="en">
        see the <span class="text-[#FF3158] underline">advantages</span> of
        being an RD
      </span>
    </h2>
    <div
      class="grid lg:grid-cols-4 sm:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 items-stretch gap-x-8 gap-y-6"
    >
      <BenefitsCard type="pen">
        <p>
          <span class="pt-BR">
            <span class="text-[#FF3158]">3 horas de revisões</span> ao vivo
            baseadas em questões toda segunda e quarta à noite ministradas em
            português.
          </span>
          <span class="en">
            <span class="text-[#FF3158]">3 hours of live</span>
             question-based reviews every Monday and Wednesday night held in
            Portuguese.
          </span>
        </p>
      </BenefitsCard>
      <BenefitsCard type="people">
        <p>
          <span class="pt-BR">
            RD produtividade: <span class="text-[#FF3158]">Mentoria 1:1</span>
             de estudos, produtividade e otimização de tempo para adequar o
            cronograma de estudos à sua rotina.
          </span>
          <span class="en">
            RD productivity: <span class="text-[#FF3158]">1:1 mentoring</span>
             of studies, productivity and time optimization to adapt the study
            schedule to your routine.
          </span>
        </p>
      </BenefitsCard>
      <BenefitsCard type="graduate">
        <p>
          <span class="pt-BR">
            <span class="text-[#FF3158]">Curso extensivo</span>
             para o STEP 1 em inglês e português com didática simples e sistema
            de revisões constantes, lecionado por professores com as maiores
            notas do Brasil e residentes nas maiores instituições americanas.
          </span>
          <span class="en">
            <span class="text-[#FF3158]">Extensive course</span> for STEP 1 in
            English and Portuguese with simple didactics and constant review
            system, taught by professors with the highest scores in Brazil and
            residents in the top American institutions.
          </span>
        </p>
      </BenefitsCard>
      <BenefitsCard type="chart">
        <p>
          <span class="pt-BR">
            A RD med procura as melhores <span class="text-[#FF3158]"
              >oportunidades de estágios</span
            > de acordo com o seu perfil, cuida do seu currículo e documentação
            e escreve os modelos de email que você precisa enviar às
            instituições.
          </span>
          <span class="en">
            RD med seeks the best <span class="text-[#FF3158]"
              >internship opportunities</span
            > according to your profile, takes care of your resume and
            documentation, and writes the email templates you need to send to
            institutions.
          </span>
        </p>
      </BenefitsCard>
    </div>
    <CTA className="self-center" href="#training">
      <span class="pt-BR">Conhecer serviços</span>
      <span class="en">Explore services</span>
    </CTA>
  </div>
  <Image
    class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 z-[2]"
    src="/images/benefits-line-pattern.png"
    alt="padrão de linhas de fundo"
    width={398}
    height={436}
    format="webp"
  />
</Section>
